  "forum_rules_body": {
    "title": "⚖️ QL7 GLOBAL FORUM RULES",
    "section_1_title": "1. GENERAL PROVISIONS",
    "section_1_1": "1.1. This document defines the terms of participation, interaction, and conduct of users within the digital space of QL7 Forum Global (hereinafter — “Forum”), which is part of the QL7 Network ecosystem and the financial-technological complex QCoin.",
    "section_1_2": "1.2. A user who logs in, publishes, or views content on the Forum automatically confirms their agreement with these Rules and undertakes to comply with them.",
    "section_1_3": "1.3. The Forum operates on the principles of openness, communication ethics, respect for other participants, compliance with the laws of all jurisdictions, and technological security within the QL7 Chain network.",
    "section_1_4": "1.4. All participants must act in good faith, respect the rights of other users, and observe intellectual, digital, and financial norms of interaction within the ecosystem.",
    "section_2_title": "2. PROHIBITED ACTIONS",
    "section_2_1": "2.1. The use of obscene, offensive, derogatory, discriminatory, or extremist language is strictly prohibited, including but not limited to statements based on nationality, race, gender, politics, or religion.",
    "section_2_2": "2.2. The distribution of sexual, pornographic, violent, or otherwise immoral or illegal content is prohibited.",
    "section_2_3": "2.3. It is forbidden to publish materials containing viruses, malicious scripts, harmful links, software backdoors, or any attempt to interfere with QL7 Network servers.",
    "section_2_4": "2.4. Spam activity, intrusive advertising, mass mailings, phishing, personal data collection, and any use of automated bots without written permission from the administration are strictly prohibited.",
    "section_2_5": "2.5. Users are forbidden to impersonate others, use someone else’s accounts, or present themselves as QL7 employees, partners, administrators, or moderators without verified status.",
    "section_2_6": "2.6. Interference with the forum’s economic processes, artificial generation of activity, manipulation of the reward system, quests, ratings, and QCoin mining is prohibited.",
    "section_2_7": "2.7. It is forbidden to create or distribute false information, manipulate public opinion, incite panic, spread disinformation, or undermine the reputation of QL7 Global.",
    "section_2_8": "2.8. Political, religious, or propagandistic activity of any kind on the Forum is not permitted.",
    "section_2_9": "2.9. Any attempt to undermine the security of the QL7 Chain blockchain, interfere with smart contracts, APIs, tokenomics, or other digital processes will be regarded as a cybercrime.",
    "section_3_title": "3. MEASURES OF RESPONSIBILITY",
    "section_3_1": "3.1. For violation of these Rules, the Administration reserves the right to restrict, temporarily suspend, or permanently block the User’s access to the Forum and all related services.",
    "section_3_2": "3.2. In cases of serious violations (posting prohibited content, hacking, spam, discrimination, destructive activity), the Administration has the right to annul balances, tokens, and exclude the account from the reward system.",
    "section_3_3": "3.3. The user bears personal responsibility for publications, comments, reposts, and actions made from their account.",
    "section_3_4": "3.4. In case of detected financial violations (money laundering, manipulations, abuse of the VIP or QCoin programs), QL7 Network reserves the right to provide the data to relevant regulatory authorities.",
    "section_4_title": "4. ETHICS AND INTERACTION",
    "section_4_1": "4.1. All forum participants must show respect toward other users, avoid confrontation and provocation.",
    "section_4_2": "4.2. The use of sarcasm, trolling, passive aggression, and any manipulative communication forms is prohibited.",
    "section_4_3": "4.3. It is recommended to use the official language of the forum — English, or the language of the current section. The use of auto-translators is encouraged for international interaction.",
    "section_5_title": "5. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY",
    "section_5_1": "5.1. All materials posted by users must belong to them or include proper attribution and copyright information.",
    "section_5_2": "5.2. Copying, reposting, modification, and distribution of content without the consent of the author and administration are prohibited.",
    "section_5_3": "5.3. All intellectual and technological property related to QL7 Forum, QL7 Network, QCoin, and L7-Chain is the exclusive property of the developer company.",
    "section_6_title": "6. FORUM FEATURES AND QCOIN ECONOMY",
    "section_6_1": "6.1. The Forum is a part of the QL7 digital economy, uniting education, social interaction, crypto-assets, and next-generation financial technologies.",
    "section_6_2": "6.2. Each user can:",
    "section_6_2_a": "— create posts, engage in dialogues, and share media;",
    "section_6_2_b": "— study in the QL7 Academy section;",
    "section_6_2_c": "— participate in quests, missions, and themed contests;",
    "section_6_2_d": "— earn QCoin for activity: likes, replies, reposts, and views.",
    "section_6_3": "6.3. VIP users receive:",
    "section_6_3_a": "— a double multiplier (x2) for QCoin mining;",
    "section_6_3_b": "— priority display of publications;",
    "section_6_3_c": "— increased rewards for quests;",
    "section_6_3_d": "— early access to new L7-Chain functions and exclusive forum events.",
    "section_6_4": "6.4. The QL7 reward system operates on an algorithmic basis: user activities are processed by neural and blockchain mechanisms ensuring transparency and precision of accruals.",
    "section_6_5": "6.5. In the future, a new blockchain order — L7-Chain — will be launched within the ecosystem, ensuring economic independence, distributed data storage, and full integration of all QL7 users into the global digital economy.",
    "section_7_title": "7. FINANCIAL SECURITY",
    "section_7_1": "7.1. All transactions involving QCoin take place through official QL7 Network channels and L7-Chain smart contracts.",
    "section_7_2": "7.2. The user must personally ensure the security of their crypto-wallets, keys, and access means.",
    "section_7_3": "7.3. The Administration is not responsible for any loss of funds due to user negligence, phishing, hacking, or third-party services.",
    "section_8_title": "8. ADMINISTRATION AND MONITORING",
    "section_8_1": "8.1. The forum administration reserves the right to amend these rules without prior notice.",
    "section_8_2": "8.2. Any actions violating community balance or posing security threats may be stopped without explanation.",
    "section_8_3": "8.3. The Forum uses automated moderation systems and behavior analysis algorithms to maintain a civilized space.",
    "section_9_title": "9. FINAL PROVISIONS",
    "section_9_1": "9.1. These Rules are legally binding for all users.",
    "section_9_2": "9.2. All changes come into effect from the moment of publication on the QL7 Forum Global platform.",
    "section_9_3": "9.3. By continuing to use the forum, the user confirms that they have read these Rules, understand the consequences of violations, and accept all terms of participation in the QL7 digital ecosystem.",
    "footer": "💠 QL7 Forum Global — a single point of the future for communication, economy, and technology. Your activity shapes not only your rating but also the image of a new financial era."
  },
