  "metamarket_info_collection_meta_space_details": "The MetaCosmos collection is one of the largest, rarest and most foundational branches of MetaMarket, dedicated to the infinite space of the future digital universe of Quantum L7 AI, Quantum Universe, Quantum Metaverse and QL7 GameVerse. It is not just a set of cosmic images, but a digital map of a vast metaspace where every element may become part of future worlds, game zones, energy systems, planetary territories, cosmic events and entire civilization branches. 🌌🪐⚡\n\nInside MetaCosmos there may exist real and imagined cosmic elements: planets, moons, asteroids, meteorites, comets, stars, nebulae, black holes, gravitational anomalies, fragments of destroyed worlds, star systems, galactic cores, energy spheres, cosmic crystals, portals, relic objects, ancient orbital structures, shards of unknown universes and spatial elements that arrived from other dimensions.\n\nEvery object in this collection is not an ordinary item, but a potential building block of the future metaverse. Today it can be a collectible digital asset, and tomorrow it may become part of the Quantum Universe map, a rare resource zone, an energy source, an event location, a game artifact, a mission key, a fragment of a planetary system or the foundation for an entire world inside QL7 GameVerse. 💎🚀\n\nMetaCosmos reveals digital ownership on a new level. An asteroid can become a resource source, a comet a symbol of an event, a planet a future territory, a nebula a zone of power, a black hole a portal between layers of reality, and a destroyed-star fragment a legendary element for a whole story. Every object receives value, rarity, owner, movement, history and a place inside Quantum L7 AI.\n\nThe collection is created for users who collect not only beautiful space objects, but pieces of future digital reality. Ownership here touches the birth of a metaverse where space, energy, economy, play, social activity and blockchain history gradually connect into one living system. 🌠\n\nOver time, MetaCosmos elements may become important parts of future mechanics: territories, routes, planetary maps, resources, factions, space expeditions, events, missions, game worlds and digital domains. Their value will unfold with the growth of Quantum L7 AI, because each object is not just a picture, but a prototype of a future world.\n\nMetaCosmos is for those who think on the scale of universes, who want to own not an item but a fragment of future space, and who understand that the true digital era begins where cosmos becomes an asset, history becomes energy, and every object becomes part of the great Quantum L7 AI metaverse. ✨🌌",
