  "metamarket_info_item_technique_aetheron_details": "✦ AETHERON. Its silhouette belongs to research rover designed for rough terrain, scans and frontier movement.\n\n◆ Visual signature: clean light, aerodynamic calm and a bright signal profile. The image gives AETHERON a personal mechanical face, so it does not dissolve into the general transport grid of MetaMarket.\n\n◇ Origin layer: It carries a trace of ether fields where sensors read not only soil, but invisible currents. The origin line gives the owner a future narrative hook for missions, routes, trade, defense or exploration.\n\n✧ Functional vector: It may become a survey platform, opening maps, resource traces and safe routes for future expeditions. The vector gives AETHERON a reason to matter beyond the image: it can influence how a user imagines movement in QL7 GameVerse.\n\n⬡ Future role: Its supply and price place it closer to accessible infrastructure, yet the object still keeps a personal serial trace. In later layers it may become part of routes, expeditions, construction arcs, defense events or elite travel scenes.\n\n◈ Owner resonance: Owning AETHERON feels like reserving a place in the transport layer of Quantum L7 AI before that layer fully opens. 🛰️",
  "metamarket_info_item_technique_aquaris_description": "AQUARIS: underwater apparatus for pressure zones and hidden routes.",
  "metamarket_info_item_technique_aquaris_details": "✦ AQUARIS. This machine carries the role of underwater apparatus for pressure zones and hidden routes.\n\n◆ Visual signature: marine glow, dense panels and a tactical water-born presence. Its visual profile is built around presence: one glance should reveal route, purpose and future status.\n\n◇ Origin layer: It comes from sealed marine programs, among sonar gates, black water and reinforced glass. Its source turns the vehicle into a fragment of infrastructure, culture and technology inside Quantum Universe.\n\n✧ Functional vector: It may become a survey platform, opening maps, resource traces and safe routes for future expeditions. The chosen function is deliberately broad, leaving room for travel, events, ownership history and future game utility.\n\n⬡ Future role: Its economics speak about a higher operational role, where function, style and limited availability meet. The asset can grow into a marker of access: not just owned, but remembered through movement, serial history and visible utility.\n\n◈ Owner resonance: AQUARIS gives the profile a technical accent, as if the user already carries their own route, hangar or command lane. 🌊",
  "metamarket_info_item_technique_aracnix_description": "ARACNIX: autonomous drone for observation, quick response and precision work.",
