  "metamarket_info_item_miscellaneous_steampen_description": "Steampen: a unique Miscellaneous artifact for future Quantum L7 AI stories.",
  "metamarket_info_item_miscellaneous_steampen_details": "✦ Steampen. A steampunk pen quill. The artifact is deliberately compact, but it can hold a bright role in social and game scenarios.\\n\\n◆ Visual signature: Color accents make the item feel connected to the wider cyber-cosmic language of MetaMarket. For Steampen, the accent reads as deliberate craft rather than random decoration.\\n\\n◇ Origin layer: The source layer is not royal or military; it is social, mobile and close to the user’s everyday legend. That origin gives Steampen a private route through the small but memorable things of Quantum Universe.\\n\\n✧ Use vector: The item is ideal for mechanics where meaning grows through transfer, timing and the identity of the owner. It can be read as a style marker, a memory token, a gift with character or a future profile detail.\\n\\n⬡ Future role: It may become a conversation starter inside future spaces where appearance, history and ownership overlap. Its future is not loud scale, but a personal place where Steampen keeps meaning through ownership and movement.\\n\\n◈ Owner resonance: It leaves the owner with a sense of having found something others passed by. The collector receives not only an object, but a compact signature with its own mood and timing. 🖋️",
  "metamarket_info_item_miscellaneous_stoneaxe_description": "Stoneaxe: a unique Miscellaneous artifact for future Quantum L7 AI stories.",
  "metamarket_info_item_miscellaneous_stoneaxe_details": "✦ Stoneaxe. An ancient stone axe. The item carries the charm of a side detail that unexpectedly becomes the center of a story.\\n\\n◆ Visual signature: Its composition is built around a clean focal point, so even a modest object feels intentional and premium. For Stoneaxe, the accent reads as deliberate craft rather than random decoration.\\n\\n◇ Origin layer: It belongs to a route of forgotten shops, service decks and hidden counters inside future megacities. That origin gives Stoneaxe a private route through the small but memorable things of Quantum Universe.\\n\\n✧ Use vector: The object may later connect to achievements, character mood, mini-events, crafting hints or community rituals. It can be read as a style marker, a memory token, a gift with character or a future profile detail.\\n\\n⬡ Future role: The object can remain affordable or rare depending on supply, but its story is designed to scale with movement. Its future is not loud scale, but a personal place where Stoneaxe keeps meaning through ownership and movement.\\n\\n◈ Owner resonance: For the owner, it marks taste, timing and attention to rare small things. The collector receives not only an object, but a compact signature with its own mood and timing. 🪓",
